  "text": "1 H-NMR spectra were recorded on a Varian Mercury spectrometer (300 MHz). Please see the 1 H-NMR of compounds 1-5 in Supplementary Materials. The optical purities of the products were measured by HPLC (Daicel Chiralcel OD-H column). 1-Phenyl-3-buten-1-ol: hexane/i-PrOH = 98:2, flow rate 1.0 mL min −1 , t R = 17.5 min (R)-enantiomer, t R = 20.9 min (S)-enantiomer [CITATION_1] . 2-Methyl-1-phenylbut-3-en-1-ol: hexanes/i-PrOH = 99:1, 0.5 mL min −1 , t R (S,S; anti) = 29.9 min, t R (S,R; syn) = 32.2 min, t R (R,R; anti) = 34.2 min, t R (R,S; syn) = 35.5 min [CITATION_2] .",
